    {
      "id": "optimistic_8_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_8",
      "description": "Ready for a dependable daily driver that won't empty your wallet? This fair-condition vehicle is a solid choice for commuters and practical-minded buyers looking for reliable transportation at a sensible price. It handles everyday driving duties well and has plenty of life left in it \u2014 just don't expect showroom perfection. If you're after honest value and straightforward transportation, this is a great fit!",
      "price": 18500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
